Class MenuItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • classes.MenuItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public abstract class MenuItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a menu item as appear on the food menu. Any menu item on a food menu has a menu name, description and price.
